data.description: Welcome to Stony Brook in the heart of Sabre Springs. This upper-unit, 1-bedroom, 1-bath home offers a prime location with breathtaking mountains, lush trees, and calm, refreshing breezes.  The interior features gleaming hardwood floors that exude warmth. The open layout creates abundant natural light to fill the space, creating a cozy and welcoming atmosphere.  Outside, you'll find your private patio, perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or unwinding after a long day. Additionally, the community offers a pool and spa, providing the ideal spot for relaxation and leisure.  Conveniently located with easy access to the 56 and 15 freeways, this home offers a central location for seamless commuting and access to all San Diego provides. You'll love the ease of walking to nearby amenities such as schools, various dining options, shopping centers, and more, making everyday living a breeze.
